{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/story_ENG.png?t=1738974437\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ve been chosen by a self-proclaimed Goddess of Life and Abundance and whisked off to another world! Just when you\u2019re ready to step up as the hero, she casually drops a bombshell: this world is going to be destroyed by the Demon Queen in 100 days.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To make matters worse, summoning you drained all of her magic. So:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She has no idea who the Demon Queen is, where they are, or how powerful they might be;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re stuck with only passive skills;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She loves using \u201cI\u2019m out of magic!\u201d as an excuse to slack off.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your quest to save the world is off to a pretty doomed\u2014and often weird\u2014start. But you\u2019re not alone: this \u201cuseless\u201d goddess is tagging along! Strangely enough, she sometimes smells\u2026 like a fish?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With only 100 days remaining, explore a world on the brink of destruction, meet unique companions, and set off on a completely unpredictable adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/character_english.png?t=1738974437\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/5_characters.gif?t=1738974437\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets